      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really frustrated because i haven't slept in two days and the meds aren't working fast enough. if i just have like 3-4 oz of wine, it's basically just a tiny bit of alcohol, right? wouldn't that just act as a boost to help the diazepam actually do its job so i can finally sleep? it feels like a lot of precaution for just a small amount of wine.",
